snippet.title: Swift 3 Fun Algorithms: Wrapping an Array
snippet.description:
Let's go ahead and take it easy for Friday by going through a relatively simple algorithm in Swift.  Hopefully this video will teach you guys a thing or two on writing a mini program that isn't all about placing things onto a screen.  

Enjoy.
